tip.text: Great food that comes in big portion which is really value for $$$. Check out the fish and chips. <3
Overpriced and the portion is really little. Frankly speaking, I tasted better nasi lemak elsewhere. Guess people just loves to join the queue.
You have to try Mao Sha Wang if you are a durian lover. Its so yummy. The waffle is good too. Try rum and raisin for alcohol fans. The alcohol level is very high!
